  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate burden of disease in Patients with newly occurred upper GI symptoms related to GERD
      (symptom frequency &amp; severity, QoL, lifestyle modifications, self-medication) - baseline data
      according to GERD impact scale presenting to specialists, especially internists

      - Evaluate effect of treatment with a acid suppressive therapy on these parameters: looking
      for improvement of symptom burden and quality of life according to the GERD impact sca
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
